V 309
Move all flake8 configuration to ``.flake8`` files

The ``.flake8`` file uses the same INI configuration format as
``tox.ini``, but allows separating test and environment configuration
from style and format configuration. It also makes it easier to
synchronise the ``.flake8`` and ``docutils/.flake8`` files.

END
